m\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10294,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/14\/ummah-split-sects-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35747,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Only the Jama&#8217;ah will go to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Afw ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Jews split into seventy-one sects, one of them is in Paradise and seventy are in the Hellfire. The Christians split into seventy-two sects, seventy-one are in the Hellfire and one of them is in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9983,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/signs-hour-slaughter-impostors\/","url_meta":{"origin":35747,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Trials: The Hour preceded by great slaughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until two groups fight each other. There will be a massive slaughter between them, although their claim is one and the same. The Hour will not be established until close\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24404,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail